{"id":4003,"date":"2025-06-09T10:44:32","date_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:44:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4003"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:44:32","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:44:32","slug":"da-khong-deu-mau-dung-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/da-khong-deu-mau-dung-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u d\u00f9ng g\u00ec? Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn, r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 t\u1eeb g\u1ed1c"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u d\u00f9ng g\u00ec?<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> L\u00e0n da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ai c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, khi\u1ebfn g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1edf n\u00ean x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 \u0103n ph\u1ea5n. V\u1eady nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u00e0 da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u d\u00f9ng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n? B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-khong-deu-mau-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb s\u1ea1m, n\u00e1m, t\u00e0n nhang, \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u ho\u1eb7c v\u00f9ng ch\u1eef T t\u1ed1i h\u01a1n c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u1edf c\u1ea3 nam v\u00e0 n\u1eef, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4005\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4005\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4005\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-1.webp\" alt=\"Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4005\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-khien-da-khong-deu-mau\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4006\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4006\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4006\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-2.webp\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4006\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00c1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi: Tia UV l\u00e0m t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t melanin &#8211; s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb s\u1ea1m m\u00e0u, n\u00e1m ho\u1eb7c t\u00e0n nhang.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1: Thay \u0111\u1ed5i hormone (do mang thai, kinh nguy\u1ec7t, thu\u1ed1c tr\u00e1nh thai\u2026) d\u1ec5 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb s\u1ea1m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau vi\u00eam (PIH): V\u1ebft th\u00e2m sau m\u1ee5n, s\u1eb9o th\u00e2m khi\u1ebfn da m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c da l\u00e3o h\u00f3a: Khi da thi\u1ebfu \u1ea9m, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u v\u00e0 bong tr\u00f3c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00d4 nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng: Thi\u1ebfu ng\u1ee7, stress, \u0103n u\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-khong-deu-mau-dung-gi-cac-nhom-hoat-chat-va-san-pham-nen-co\"><\/span><b>Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u d\u00f9ng g\u00ec? C\u00e1c nh\u00f3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00ean c\u00f3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u v\u00e0 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4004\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4004\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4004\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-Thumb.webp\" alt=\"Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u d\u00f9ng g\u00ec\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-Thumb.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-Thumb-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-Thumb-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-Thumb-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-Thumb-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4004\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u d\u00f9ng g\u00ec<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vitamin-c-%e2%80%93-lam-sang-va-chong-oxy-hoa\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin C &#8211; L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin C l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0ng gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf s\u1ea3n sinh melanin v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng: D\u00f9ng serum vitamin C bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"niacinamide-%e2%80%93-lam-sang-nhe-nhang-an-toan-cho-da-nhay-cam\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide &#8211; L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, an to\u00e0n cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide (vitamin B3) c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m n\u00e1m, \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4007\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4007\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4007\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-3.webp\" alt=\"Niacinamide - L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, an to\u00e0n cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4007\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Niacinamide &#8211; L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, an to\u00e0n cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng: C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng s\u00e1ng \u2013 t\u1ed1i, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ho\u1eb7c serum.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"habha-%e2%80%93-tay-te-bao-chet-giup-da-min-va-sang-hon\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">HA\/BHA &#8211; T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft gi\u00fap da m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u. AHA (nh\u01b0 glycolic acid) v\u00e0 BHA (salicylic acid) gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng: T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc 2\u20133 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Lu\u00f4n d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng acid.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"sua-rua-mat-diu-nhe-%e2%80%93-lam-sach-nhung-khong-gay-kho\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 &#8211; L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t. H\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH 5.5 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3791\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3791\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3791\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/21-5-3.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 x\u1eed l\u00fd vi\u00eam\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/21-5-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/21-5-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/21-5-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/21-5-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3791\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">G\u1ee3i \u00fd s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m: GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel \u2013 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 r\u00e1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kem-chong-nang-%e2%80%93-buoc-khong-the-thieu\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng &#8211; B\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng n\u00e0o ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng. Tia UV l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00e2y th\u00e2m n\u00e1m v\u00e0 x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u da. N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng SPF t\u1eeb 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean, d\u00f9ng m\u1ed7i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 b\u00f4i l\u1ea1i sau 3 &#8211; 4 ti\u1ebfng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhung-luu-y-khi-cham-soc-da-khong-deu-mau\"><\/span><b>Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4008\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4008\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4008\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-4.webp\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/35-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4008\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lu\u00f4n test s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t v\u00f9ng nh\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng to\u00e0n m\u1eb7t<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh k\u00edch \u1ee9ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c, u\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0103n nhi\u1ec1u rau xanh \u0111\u1ec3 da kh\u1ecfe t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec th\u00f3i quen \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 6\u20138 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00fang nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da v\u1edbi c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. H\u00e3y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n: l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1eb1ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, nh\u1eb9 d\u1ecbu nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m GSC+ v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n l\u00e0n da nh\u01b0 s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t pH 5.5, serum niacinamide hay kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1eady nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u00e0 da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u d\u00f9ng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n? B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4004,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4003","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4003","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4003"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4003\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4009,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4003\/revisions\/4009"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4004"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4003"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4003"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4003"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}